snippet.title: Finding the Quadrant in Which an Angle Lies - Example 1
snippet.description: Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Finding the Quadrant in Which an Angle Lies - Example 1.  In this video, I consider a few different angle (measured in degrees) and find the quadrant which they would belong to.
